messages.messageBody:
Thank you for all your great discussion on this. It was heavily posted and
heavily responded to. Regardless of what the asker thought about it, I have
had some great reflection on this issue personally.

I personally agree with the opinion that it is not a yes or no answer. It
depends on a large number of variable issues from person to person, age
being only one of those variables.

Much Love
Wildflower
